title: What a continental free trade deal would mean for African businesses
description: The anticipated Continental free trade agreement will be signed and ratified tomorrow. How is the agreement going to fast-track growth of Africa multinational companies? Michael Kottoh, Chief Stategist at Afrochampions Initiative joined CNBC Africa for more.
